# Autonocraft Test Gate

After modifying player physics, world generation, chunking, blocks, inventory, tools, skills, animals, combat, crafting, fluids, structures, or saves:

```bash
dotnet run --project src/Autonocraft -- --test
```

Or:

```bash
dotnet test tests/Autonocraft.Tests
```

All tests must pass (exit code 0) before concluding the task.

See `AGENTS.md` §3 for the full test catalog and `docs/CODEMAP.md` for test-to-subsystem mapping.
